---
source: src/tests.rs
expression: render_command_help(&refs)
---
Assert the number of elements matching a selector

Usage: bl expect count [OPTIONS] <selector> <number>

Arguments:
  <selector>  CSS selector to count matches for
  <number>    Expected number of matches

Options:
      --headless  Hide browser window (visible by default)
  -v, --verbose   Enable debug logging
      --json      Output as JSON
  -h, --help      Print help

Examples:
  bl expect count "li.item" 3
  # Pass if exactly 3 items match
